.registration-new
  .registration-new-container
    %header.registration-new-header
      %h1.registration-new-header__logo-part
        %a(href= root_path)
          = image_tag src="logo.png", size: "193x49"
    %main.registration-new-main
      .account-input-box
        .account-input-box__head
          %h2 会員情報入力
        .account-input-box__body
          = form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: registration_path(resource_name)) do |f|
            = devise_error_messages!
            .account-input-box__body__forms
              .field#field-top
                .field-label
                  = f.label :ニックネーム, class: 'field-label__name'
                  %span.form-require
                    必須
                .field-input
                  = f.text_field :nickname, autofocus: true, class: 'field-input__box'
              .field
                .field-label
                  = f.label :メールアドレス, class: 'field-label__name'
                  %span.form-require
                    必須
                .field-input
                  = f.email_field :email, class: 'field-input__box'

              .password-part
                .field
                  .field-label
                    = f.label :パスワード, class: 'field-label__name'
                    %span.form-require
                      必須
                  .field-input
                    = f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "off", class: 'field-input__box'
                .field
                  .field-label
                    = f.label :パスワード, class: 'field-label__name'
                    %span.form-require
                      必須
                  .field-input
                    = f.password_field :password_confirmation, autocomplete: "off", class: 'field-input__box'
                %p.form-info
                  ※ 英字と数字の両方を含めて設定してください
              .field
                %h3.form-info2__head
                  本人確認
                %p.form-info2__body
                  安心・安全にご利用いただくために、お客さまの本人情報の登録にご協力ください。他のお客さまに公開されることはありません。

              .field
                .field-label
                  = f.label :お名前（全角）, class: 'field-label__name'
                  %span.form-require
                    必須
                .field-input
                  = f.text_field :family_name, autofocus: true, class: 'field-input__box family-name'
                  = f.text_field :first_name, autofocus: true, class: 'field-input__box'
              .field
                .field-label
                  = f.label :お名前カナ, class: 'field-label__name'
                  %span.form-require
                    必須
                .field-input
                  = f.text_field :family_name_kana, autofocus: true, class: 'field-input__box family-name'
                  = f.text_field :first_name_kana, autofocus: true, class: 'field-input__box'
              .field
                .field-label
                  = f.label :生年月日, class: 'field-label__name'
                  %span.form-require
                    必須
                .field-input
                  = f.text_field :birthday, autofocus: true, class: 'field-input__box'
                %p.form-info
                  ※ 本人情報は正しく入力してください。会員登録後、修正するにはお時間を頂く場合があります。
            .account-input-box__body__btn-part
              .registration-new-btn
                = f.submit "登録", class: 'registration-new-btn'
              .account-input-box__body__btn-part-text1
                %p= link_to '本人情報確認について','#' ,class: 'btn-part-link'
              .account-input-box__body__btn-part-text2
                %p
                  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and the Google 
                  =link_to 'Privacy Policy','#' ,class: 'btn-part-link'
                  and 
                  =link_to 'Terms of Service','#' ,class: 'btn-part-link'
                  apply.
    %footer.registration-new-footer
      %small
        %nav.registration-new-footer__nav
          %ul.registration-new-footer__nav__ul
            %li= link_to 'プライバシーポリシー','', class: 'registration-new-footer__nav__ul__li'
            %li= link_to 'フリマ利用規約', '', class: 'registration-new-footer__nav__ul__li'
            %li= link_to '特定商取引に関する表記','', class: 'registration-new-footer__nav__ul__li'
        %a.footer-logolink
          = image_tag src="logo-white.png", size: "223x65"
        %p.footer-p
          © Gasiwatani, Inc.

          